column5: Like Moosebunk i have a picture in a facebook contest.  Winner doesn't get to go on a dream fishing vacation (i wish), but just a small fishing grab bag with some goodies.  I have entered my little girl with her first fish, although small, she wanted to take it home to eat.  Any likes would be greatyl appreciated to get here tackle collection growing!  https://www.facebook.com/HiwayVariety/photos/a.801010739946091.1073741870.483776768336158/801202189926946/?type=3&theater  Thanks Anders
